Package tum.dss.thesis.knapsack

This package is a concrete implementation of the LS framework for multi-unit auctions (respectively multi-parameter knapsack problems).

See: Description

    GreedyAlgorithm

Package tum.dss.thesis.knapsack Description

This package is a concrete implementation of the LS framework for multi-unit auctions (respectively multi-parameter knapsack problems). In order to adapt the LS framework to another problem all classes in this packages need to be defined and implemented for the new problem.
Author:
Florian Stallmann
